---
title: Cajun Blackened Turkey and Roasted Potatoes with Green Bean Salad
description: If you're going to have a salad for dinner, make it this one! Tender turkey, potatoes, fresh green beans, tomatoes and a creamy dressing come together in the ultimate power salad!
